## Welcome Adventurer !
<br><br>
Dungeons and Dragons Spellbook is a webapp that let you visualize all the different spells available for the role playing game DnD [Official website](https://dnd.wizards.com/).

From the left navigation panel you'll have access to the either the spell tree visualisation, the spell comparator or the raw data extractor

This webapp was developped using [shiny](https://shiny.rstudio.com/) <br>
The code is available on [github](https://github.com/DnDViz/Main_Project_DnD). 

For a quick explanation of what is dungeons and dragons.
